   "source": [
    "<div style='background:#4a4a4a;color:white;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:6px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "4 &middot; Model 2: Transfer Learning via ResNet-50\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style='padding:16px 6px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#000;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Methodology:** Transfer Learning using a heavy deep Residual Network backbone pre-trained on the ImageNet corpus (1.28 million natural image records).\n",
    "- **Training Paradigm:** \n",
    "  - **Phase 1 (Frozen Backbone):** Linear Probe focusing solely on adjusting a fresh, randomly initialized Fully Connected Head for 15 baseline epochs.\n",
    "  - **Phase 2 (Planned Strategy):** Full Network discriminative learning rate unfreezing to globally map custom road-sign domains smoothly.\n",
    "\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<div style='background:#4a4a4a;color:white;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:6px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "5 &middot; Benchmarks, Empirical Analysis & Results\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top:15px; font-weight:bold; color:#000;'>\n",
    "  <tr style='background:#f2f2f2; border-bottom:2px solid #ccc;'>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Model Architecture</th>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Parameter Size</th>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Test Accuracy Result</th>\n",
    "    <th style='padding:10px; text-align:left;'>Inference Compute Latency</th>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "  <tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px; color:#1e824c;'>Model 1: Custom Deep CNN</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>~460K parameters</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px; color:#1e824c; font-size:18px;'>98.71%</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Extremely Lightweight / Ultra-Fast</td>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "  <tr style='border-bottom:1px solid #eee;'>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px; color:#b8860b;'>Model 2: ResNet-50 (Head Only)</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>~23.5M parameters</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px; color:#b8860b;'>79.82%</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Heavier Structural Computational Burden</td>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "  <tr style='border-bottom:2px solid #ccc; background:#fafafa;'>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Human Baseline Control</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>N/A</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>98.84%</td>\n",
    "    <td style='padding:10px;'>Variable baseline response constraints</td>\n",
    "  </tr>\n",
    "</table>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style='margin-top:15px; padding:14px; background:#fdf2e9; border-left:5px solid #e67e22; border-radius:4px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#000; font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "  <span style='color:#d35400; font-size:16px;'>&#128161; Critical Analysis - The ResNet Paradox:</span><br>\n",
    "  Why did the giant ResNet-50 (79.82%) trail behind our small Custom CNN (98.71%)? <br>\n",
    "  1. <strong>Feature Mismatch Constraints:</strong> The frozen ImageNet features are heavily optimized for natural everyday scale objects (dogs, cars, cups), missing the specialized spatial details required for fine-grained traffic sign internal texts and borders.<br>\n",
    "  2. <strong>Frozen Layer Bottleneck:</strong> Restricting optimization exclusively to the linear head for only 15 epochs did not give the model sufficient capacity to adapt. Global unfreezing (Full Fine-Tuning) is required to unlock ResNet's true generalization capability.\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<div style='background:#4a4a4a;color:white;padding:14px 22px;border-radius:6px;font-size:20px;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "6 &middot; Conclusion & Future Directions\n",
    "</div>\n",
    "\n",
    "<div style='padding:16px 6px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#000;font-weight:bold;'>\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Custom CNN Success:** Our lightweight model achieved **98.71%**, performing virtually neck-and-neck with the absolute Human Baseline Control (98.84%).\n",
    "- **Core Engineering Takeaway:** Heavy models are not magic bullets; task-specific architecture design paired with rigorous regularization (Stratified data, Dropout2d, Label Smoothing) often defeats raw model size on specialized tasks.\n",
    "- **Future Milestones:** Real-time embedded edge deployment (INT8 Model Quantization) and adversarial attacks robustness evaluations ($\epsilon$-FGSM resistance testing).\n",
    "\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
